Question: What do you like/dislike about public transportation.
Answer:
The good side of public transportation is that they are very cheap, as long as the public transportation is developed, it is very convenient. It is also good for the environment since less car will be on the street if people choose to use public transportation. It has bad side too: most public transportation is slower than a private car, and they cannot be used whenever you want to use them because they have their own schedule.